Ukraine's%20energy%20sector%20--%20something%20it%20called%20a%20response%20to%20Ukraine%20firing%20US%20and%20British%20supplied%20missiles%20on%20Russian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20to%20stop%20the%20hot%20stage%20of%20the%20war%2C%20we%20should%20take%20under%20NATO%20umbrella%20the%20territory%20of%20Ukraine%20that%20we%20have%20under%20our%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20told%20Britain's%20Sky%20News%2C%20according%20to%20a%20voiceover%20translation%20of%20his%20remarks%20from%20Ukrainian%20into%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do%20fast%2C%20and%20then%20Ukraine%20can%20get%20back%20the%20other%20part%20of%20its%20territory%20diplomatically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalk%20of%20a%20possible%20ceasefire%20or%20peace%20deal%20has%20ratched%20up%20since%20Donald%20Trump%20won%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20has%20criticised%20US%20aid%20to%20Kyiv%20and%20claimed%20he%20could%20halt%20the%20conflict%20within%20hours%2C%20without%20saying%20how.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20controls%20around%2018%20percent%20of%20Ukraine's%20internationally%20recognised%20territory%2C%20including%20the%20Crimean%20peninsula%20which%20Moscow%20annexed%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20invading%20in%202022%2C%20Moscow%20has%20claimed%20four%20more%20eastern%20and%20southern%20regions%20of%20Ukraine%20--%20Donetsk%2C%20Kherson%2C%20Lugansk%20and%20Zaporizhzhia%20--%20as%20its%20own%2C%20despite%20not%20having%20full%20control%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKyiv%20has%20repeatedly%20ruled%20out%20ceding%20territory%20in%20exchange%20for%20peace%2C%20while%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20demanded%20Ukraine's%20army%20withdraw%20from%20swathes%20more%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Guarantees'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20insisted%20any%20offer%20to%20join%20NATO%20must