0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaunching-an-e-commerce-business-step-one-finding-business-partner-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etry%20my%20hand%20at%20launching%20and%20selling%20a%20product%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20brought%20a%20friend%20and%20former%20roommate%20on%20board%2C%20and%20in%20April%202024%2C%20we%20deposited%20%2410%2C000%20into%20a%20business%20checking%20account%20to%20bring%20our%20product%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilding-an-ecommerce-business-how-to-select-a-profitable-product-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epickleball%20paddles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20to%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDepositing%20funds%20was%20the%20easy%20part.%20The%20building-the-business%20part%20has%20been%20a%20tedious%20challenge%20that%20started%20nearly%20two%20years%20ago%20in%20the%20living%20room%20of%20our%20Los%20Angeles%20apartment%20when%20we%20first%20began%20tossing%20product%20ideas%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20both%20work%20full-time%20jobs%20and%20figured%20outsourcing%20certain%20tasks%20would%20be%20key.%20While%20we%20were%20willing%20to%20commit%20some%20weekday%20nights%20and%20weekends%20to%20our%20side%20project%2C%20we%20didn't%20want%20it%20to%20feel%20all-consuming.%20We%20also%20know%20what%20we're%20good%20at%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20perhaps%20more%20importantly%2C%20we%20know%20what%20we're%20not%20so%20good%20at.%20Creating%20a%20high-quality%20brand%20and%20product%20that%20we%20were%20proud%20of%20would%20mean%20hiring%20smart%2C%20talented%20people%20to%20help%20with%20the%20stuff%20we're%20not%20great%20at.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere's%20everything%20we've%20outsourced%20so%20far%20to%20get%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F615f61-5b.myshopify.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPeak%20Pickleball%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20up%20and%20running.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EProduct%20sourcing.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20product%20is%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20business%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20only%20offer%20one%20%E2%80%94%20so%20nailing%20the%20design%20was%20crucial.%20I'd%20learned%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-seller-how-to-run-successful-profitable-online-ecommerce-business-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterviewing%20top%20Amazon%20sellers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20finding%20a%20reliable%20supplier%20would%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20project%20when%20we%20were%20still%20messing%20around%20with%20different%20product%20ideas%2C%20we%20used%20Alibaba%20to%20connect%20with%20suppliers%20and%20start%20to%20understand%20manufacturing%20costs.%20There%20were%20endless%20suppliers%20to%20choose%20from%20who%20were%20all%20quick%20to%20message%20back%20and%20eager%20to%20work%20with%20us%2C%20but%20we%20were%20hesitant%20to%20proceed.%20The%20language%20barrier%20was%20evident%20and%20the%20thought%20of%20eventually%20sending%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20overseas%20to%20buy%20inventory%20from%20a%20supplier%20we'd%20never%20met%20was%20nervewracking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peak%20pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672a60c65ec9bfa3d63bd8ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrototypes%20arrived%20at%20the%20author's%20apartment%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUltimately%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20work%20with%20a%20product-sourcing%20company%20founded%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sell-on-amazon-succeed-start-side-hustle-ecommerce-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EeCommerce%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Joe%20Reeves.%20He's%20familiar%20with%20the%20challenges%20of%20finding%20a%20good%2C%20trustworthy%20supplier%2C%20having%20gone%20through%20the%20process%20himself%20when%20launching%20his%20wallet%20business.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EReeves%20started%20the%20company%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.330trading.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E330%20Trading%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20a%20college%20friend%20who%20lives%20in%20Taipei%20and%20is%20on%20the%20ground%20communicating%20in%20person%20with%20various%20factories%20in%20Asia%2C%20including%20the%20one%20that%20is%20manufacturing%20our%20pickleball%20paddle%20and%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EPackaging%20design.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20hired%20a%20freelance%20designer%20through%20Fiverr%20to%20help%20design%20our%20packaging.%20We%20had%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20we%20wanted%20it%20to%20look%20like%20but%20didn't%20have%20the%20skills%20(or%20bandwidth%20to%20learn%20the%20skills%20necessary)%20to%20execute%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peak%20pickleball%20packaging%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674792099f2901eb603779ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Fiverr%20freelancer%20helped%20the%20Peak%20cofounders%20design%20the%20packaging.%3Cp%3E330%20Trading%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWebsite.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20also%20outsourced%20web%20design%2C%20which%20neither%20of%20us%20had%20experience%20with%2C%20and%20hired%20a%20different%20freelancer%20through%20Fiverr%20to%20put%20together%20a%20basic%20Shopify%20website.%20Moving%20forward%2C%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20do%20site%20upkeep%20ourselves%2C%20but%20hiring%20someone%20to%20create%20a%20clean%2C%20compelling%20homepage%20and%20build%20out%20the%20other%20main%20pages%20was%20well%20worth%20%24158.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ced5ae1b-4023-4f30-b04b-8105ae4f0db2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20best%20%24250%20we%20spent%3A%20Outsourcing%20logo%20design%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20nearly%20%246%2C000%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lanch-ecommerce-company-startup-costs-expenses-business-budget-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20startup%20costs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Some%20of%20those%20costs%20were%20unavoidable%2C%20like%20the%20%2439%20a%20month%20we%20pay%20for%20Shopify%20Basic%2C%20while%20others%20were%20more%20of%20a%20choice%3A%20We%20spent%20about%20%242%2C500%20to%20get%20our%20paddle%20approved%20by%20USA%20Pickleball%20so%20that%20it%20can%20be%20used%20in%20USAP-sanctioned%20tournaments.%20We're%20betting%20on%20the%20pricey%20stamp%20of%20approval%2C%20which%20also%20helps%20legitimize%20our%20brand%2C%20paying%20off%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20costs%20that%20we%20outsourced%20technically%20weren't%20necessary%2C%20but%20they%20saved%20us%20time%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20improved%20our%20product.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20expense%20that%20we%20outsourced%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20feels%20fully%20worth%20the%20cost%3A%20We%20hired%20a%20professional%20graphic%20designer%20to%20develop%20our%20logo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peak%20pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67479279ede4eeae392a2a00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20graphic%20designer%20helped%20develop%20the%20triple-layered%20%26quot%3BP%26quot%3B%20logo.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Monds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20worked%20with%20a%20friend%20we%20knew%20well%20and%20trusted%20fully.%20It%20was%20a%20back-and-forth%20process%20that%20started%20with%20us%20answering%20five%20branding%20questions%20she%20emailed%20to%20us%20ahead%20of%20our%20first%20meeting%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20are%20some%20adjectives%20to%20describe%20how%20you%20want%20your%20brand%20to%20come%20across%3F%20Or%20how%20you%20want%20people%20to%20feel%20when%20interacting%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20there%20a%20few%20brands%20that%20you%20both%20really%20admire%20(for%20messaging%2C%20logo%2C%20brand%20activity%2C%20etc.)%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20than%20on%20the%20paddle%20where%20else%20can%20you%20envision%20the%20logo%20being%20used%2Finteracted%20with%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EDo%20you%20envision%20brand%20activity%20beyond%20selling%20paddles%20and%20the%20marketing%20efforts%20to%20support%20that%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20are%20the%20spec%20sizes%2Frequirements%20for%20branding%20relative%20to%20the%20prototype%20paddle%20specifically%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESitting%20down%20and%20talking%20through%20our%20answers%20helped%20us%20nail%20down%20the%20identity%20of%20our%20brand%3A%20We%20are%20energetic%2C%20playful%2C%20and%20innovative%20%E2%80%94%20and%20our%20designer%20created%20a%20logo%20and%20color%20palette%20that%20represents%20who%20Peak%20Pickleball%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20paid%20%24250%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20best%20money%20we've%20spent%20on%20the%20business%20to%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-ecommerce-company-tasks-worth-paying-to-outsource-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732968841000%2C%22vis