%20called%20to%20his%20home%20on%20Tarbat%20Road%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20May%206%2C%20Tarnjeet%20was%20already%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarnjeet%2C%2044%2C%20was%20found%20with%20extensive%20trauma%20to%20her%20face%2C%20as%20well%20as%20multiple%20broken%20ribs%2C%20when%20she%20was%20found%20unresponsive%20by%20the%20emergency%20services%2C%20who%20had%20been%20called%20by%20Sidpara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Sidpara%20admitted%20the%20lesser%20manslaughter%20charge%20of%20causing%20the%20injuries%20to%20his%20girlfriend%20but%20denied%20intending%20to%20kill%20her%20or%20cause%20her%20serious%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20that%20his%20victim%20was%20left%20with%20%26quot%3Btwo%20enormous%20black%20eyes%26quot%3B%2C%20bleeding%20on%20the%20brain%20and%2020%20rib%20fractures%2C%20among%20other%20injuries.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20steadfastly%20refused%20to%20explain%20what%20you%20did%20or%20why%2C%26quot%3B%20Judge%20William%20Harbage%20said%2C%20addressing%20the%20accused%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20clear%20is%20that%20you%20attacked%20her%20in%20a%20savage%20and%20merciless%20way%3B%20you%20punched%2C%20kicked%20and%20stamped%20on%20her%20in%20a%20sustained%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BBC%20court%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20that%20Sidpara%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20alcohol%20dependence%20syndrome%20and%20had%2024%20previous%20convictions%20for%2046%20offences%2C%20including%20threats%20to%20kill%20and%20harassment%20of%20previous%20girlfriends%20and%20people%20connected%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESidpara's%20sentencing%20comes%20as%20Leicestershire%20Police%20said%20it%20has%20joined%20organisations%20across%20the%20globe%20to%20support%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Ribbon%20Day%26quot%3B%2C%20focussed%20on%20targeted%20action%20around%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTarnjeet%20was%20killed%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20someone%20she%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with.%20Someone%20who%20should%20have%20supported%20and%20protected%20her%2C%20not%20someone%20she%20should%20have%20feared%20would%20brutally%20attack%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Senior%20Investigating%20Officer%20Detective%20Inspector%20Emma%20Matts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20person%20responsible%20will%20now%20spend%20many%20years%20behind%20bars%2C%20Tarnjeet's%20family%20are%20left%20with%20so%20many%20questions%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20feeling%20of%20wondering%20if%20they%20could%20have%20done%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20domestic%20abuse%20is%20very%20complex.%20Often%20victims%20don't%20want%20to%20share%20with%20family%20and%20friends%20the%20details%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%20let%20alone%20with%20police%2C%20but%20it%20is%20vital%20anyone%20suffering%20gets%20the%20support%20they%20need%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20abuse%20before%20it%20is%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732968660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fatt9hsso_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F50-year-old-indian-origin-man-gets-life-term-for-girlfriends-murder-in-uk-7141353%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-origin%20man%20who%20brutally%20beat%20up%20his%20girlfriend%20to%20death%20at%20his%20home%20in%20East%20Midlands%20region%20of%20England%2C%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20by%20a%20UK%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F50-year-old-indian-origin-man-gets-life-term-for-girlfriends-murder-in-uk-7141353%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%2