0it%20everywhere%2C%20zipping%20around%20rather%20than%20sitting%20in%20a%20stroller.%20When%20tons%20of%20people%20asked%20me%20about%20the%20bike%2C%20I%20realized%20there%20was%20a%20business%20opportunity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20a%20lifelong%20entrepreneur%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20tourism%2C%20real%20estate%20investment%2C%20and%20mountain%20biking.%20When%20I%20founded%20Strider%2C%20I%20owned%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fdocuments-needed-for-mortgage-application%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emortgage%20brokerage%20firm%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20For%20the%20first%20two%20years%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20Strider%20during%20nights%20and%20weekends%20while%20my%20sons%20zipped%20around%20the%20workshop%20on%20their%20bikes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20very%20challenging%2C%20but%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20it%20has%20become%20very%20lucrative.%20Today%2C%20I'm%2056%2C%20and%20my%20net%20worth%20is%20about%20%2430%20million.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225424a75c-e98a-45c5-999f-04f7c05c30f0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20want%20to%20help%20my%20sons%20but%20not%20do%20anything%20for%20them%20fully%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-in-estate-planning-it-makes-me-appreciate-my-family-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestate%20planning%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20have%20had%20many%20discussions%20about%20what%20to%20do%20with%20our%20wealth.%20We've%20decided%20we%20want%20to%20help%20the%20boys%2C%20but%20not%20doing%20anything%20for%20them%20entirely.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20believe%20a%20full%20and%20well-rounded%20life%20shouldn't%20be%20easy%20or%20comfortable%20all%20the%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5