ly%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20peaceful%20demonstrations%20led%20by%20the%20Hindu%20community%20to%20protect%20themselves.%20These%20protests%2C%20which%20are%20a%20democratic%20response%20to%20violence%2C%20are%20being%20met%20with%20increasing%20repression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20the%20RSS%20condemned%20the%20unjust%20imprisonment%20of%20ISKCON%20monk%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%2C%20who%20has%20been%20leading%20peaceful%20protests%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20arrest%20of%20a%20religious%20leader%20who%20is%20advocating%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20Hindus%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20Bangladesh%20government%20to%20ensure%20the%20immediate%20cessation%20of%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20and%20to%20release%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20from%20prison.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20RSS%20urged%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20continue%20its%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20the%20persecution%20of%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20to%20take%20swift%20action%20to%20build%20global%20support%20for%20the%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20critical%20juncture%2C%20the%20RSS%20called%20on%20India%20and%20the%20global%20community%20to%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20victims%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20urging%20their%20respective%20governments%20to%20take%20every%20possible%20measure%20to%20end%20these%20atrocities%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20world%20peace%20and%20brotherhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20expressing%20concern%20over%20the%20rise%20of%20%26quot%3Bextremist%20rhetoric%2C%20increasing%20incidents%20of%20violence%20and%20provocation%26quot%3B%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20India%20has%20consistently%20and%20strongly%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20targeted%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%20with%20Bangladesh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5