20where%20she%20died%20around%206.30%20am%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurga%20Mahanto's%20father%2C%20Ram%20Pravesh%20Mahanto%2C%20said%20that%20after%20taking%20some%20medicines%20one%20of%20the%20children%20got%20better%20but%20Durga's%20condition%20kept%20getting%20worse.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20even%20know%20how%20did%20this%20happen.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20back%20home%20from%20work%20I%20saw%20the%20girls%20and%20then%20took%20them%20to%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20at%20the%20Navsari%20hospital%2C%20the%20staff%20told%20them%20that%20the%20girls%20needed%20to%20be%20tested%20but%20the%20blood%20reports%20would%20only%20come%20on%20Monday%2C%20as%20the%20lab%20is%20closed%20on%20Saturdays%20and%20Sundays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurat%20Civil%20Hospital%20Chief%20Medical%20Officer%20Dr%20Ketan%20Naik%20said%20the%20girls%20might%20have%20fallen%20ill%20after%20inhaling%20the%20toxic%20fumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20some%20of%20the%20girls%20also%20had%20eaten%20ice%20cream%20at%20night%2C%20so%20there%20was%20also%20a%20possibility%20of%20food%20poisoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20will%20become%20clear%20after%20postmortem%20and%20forensic%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Mahendra%20Prasad%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732966860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ff394mk2o_bonfire-generic_625x300_30_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-girls-playing-around-garbage-bonfire-die-of-gas-poisoning-in-gujarat-surat-7141027%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20girls%20were%20playing%20around%20a%20bonfire%20in%20Gujarat's%20Surat%20on%20Friday%20evening.%20Hours%20later%2C%20three%20were%20dead%20leaving%20two%20survivors%20to%20tell%20the%20nightmarish%20tale%20that%20led%20up%20to%20their%20deaths.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22eng