ot%3BWe%20are%20not%20just%20individuals%20in%20parliament%2C%20but%20more%20than%20that%20we%20embody%20the%20sentiment%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad.%20They%20have%20placed%20their%20trust%20in%20us%2C%20believed%20in%20us%2C%20and%20acknowledged%20that%20we%20represent%20their%20feelings%20in%20the%20parliament%20of%20India.%20Our%20top%20priority%20is%20to%20represent%20the%20sentiment%20that%20has%20sent%20us%20to%20parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20elder%20of%20the%20two%20siblings%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20said%20in%20English%2C%20which%20a%20translator%20repeated%20in%20Malayalam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20see%20a%20child%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20I%20am%20reminded%20that%20their%20parents%20have%20sent%20me%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20care%20for%20them.%20%C2%A0If%20I%20can%20bring%20a%20smile%20to%20their%20faces%2C%20I%20should%20do%20it%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20earlier%20represented%20Wayanad%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20After%20he%20won%20the%20general%20election%20this%20year%20from%20both%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Raebareli%20and%20Wayanad%2C%20he%20chose%20the%20constituency%20in%20UP%2C%20which%20necessitated%20a%20by-election%20in%20the%20Kerala%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20are%20sitting%20in%20parliament%2C%20we%20have%20to%20realise%20that%20of%20course%2C%20we%20are%20individuals.%20Priyanka%20is%20an%20individual%20and%20Rahul%20is%20an%20individual%20taking%20oath%2C%20but%20actually%20more%20than%20an%20individual%20we%20are%20feeling%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wayanad%20constituency%20comprises%20seven%20assembly%20segments%20of%20Mananthavady%20(Scheduled%20Tribes)%2C%20Sulthan%20Bathery%20(Scheduled%20Tribes)%2C%20and%20Kalpetta%20in%20Wayanad%20district%3B%20Thiruvambady%20in%20Kozhikode%20dis