discipline%20are%20called%20for%20now%20more%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CWC%20resolution%20read.%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20must%20keep%20reinforcing%20its%20narrative.%20This%20includes%20caste%20census%20to%20ensure%20full%20social%20justice%2C%20removal%20of%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20ceiling%20on%20reservations%20for%20scheduled%20castes%2C%20scheduled%20tribes%20and%20OBCs%2C%20control%20of%20growing%20monopolies%20in%20the%20economy%20through%20political%20patronage%20and%20continuing%20price%20rise%20and%20growing%20unemployment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20announced%20plans%20for%20a%20nationwide%20movement%20in%20collaboration%20with%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20to%20address%20concerns%20over%20the%20electoral%20process.%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20the%20party's%20general%20secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20communications%2C%20stated%20that%20rallies%20would%20soon%20be%20organised%20to%20mobilise%20public%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732962480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fevtgdo08_rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge-ani-_625x300_30_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcrack-the-whip-rahul-gandhis-request-to-m-kharge-after-maharashtra-rout-7140674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Back-to-back%20electoral%20defeats%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20have%20prompted%20calls%20for%20introspection%20and%20decisive%20action%20in%20the%20Congress%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcrack-the-whip-rahul-gandhis-request-to-m-kharge-after-maharashtra-rout-7140674%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20counting%20underway%2C%20here's%20what%20to%20look%20out%20for%20in%20Ireland's%20general%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732962120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F11%2F192