dia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchristmas-vibes-janhvi-and-khushi-kapoor-share-heartwarming-sibling-moment%2Farticleshow%2F115839145.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBCCI%2C%20PCB%20Need%20More%20Time...%26quot%3B%3A%20Pak%20Great%20Provides%20Big%20Champions%20Trophy%20Update%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Rashid%20Latif%20claimed%20that%20the%20ICC%20Board%20meeting%20to%20finalise%20the%20venues%20and%20schedule%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20will%20be%20held%20either%20on%20Sunday%20or%20the%20day%20after.%20The%20ICC%20Governing%20Board%20meeting%20on%20Friday%20failed%20to%20reach%20any%20consensus%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20meeting%20was%20held%20over%20an%20online%20call%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20all%2015%20members%20of%20the%20board%20-%2012%20full%20members%20representatives%20and%20three%20Associate%20nations%20directors%20%E2%80%93%20in%20attendance%20along%20with%20CEO%20Geoff%20Allardice%20and%20Chairman%20Greg%20Barclay.%20The%20former%20Pakistani%20cricketer%20said%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20and%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20need%20time%20to%20discuss%20with%20their%20external%20affairs%20ministries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeadlock.%20As%20per%20information%20there%20is%20no%20ICC%20emergency%20Board%20meeting%20today%2C%20It%20will%20be%20tomorrow%20or%20the%20day%20after..%20BCCI%20and%20PCB%20need%20more%20time%20to%20discuss%20with%20foreign%20ministries%2C%26quot%3B%20Latif%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20played%20from%20February%2019%20to%20March%209.%20But%20it%20has%20run%20into%20uncertainty%20after%20BCCI%20said%20it%20did%20not%20have%20the%20Indian%20government's%20consent%20to%20travel%20and%20play%20its%20matches%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2F