20and%20arrested%20the%20director%20of%20a%20gay%20travel%20agency%20under%20laws%20criminalising%20%26quot%3BLGBT%20propaganda%26quot%3B%2C%20state%20media%20reported.%20Russian%20security%20forces%20raided%20at%20least%20three%20bars%20and%20nightclubs%20overnight%20%26quot%3Bas%20part%20of%20measures%20to%20combat%20LGBT%20propaganda%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20state%20TASS%20news%20agency%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpolice-in-moscow-raid-bars-over-lgbt-propaganda%2Farticleshow%2F115839186.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpolice-in-moscow-raid-bars-over-lgbt-propaganda%2Famp_articleshow%2F115839186.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpolice-in-moscow-raid-bars-over-lgbt-propaganda%2Famp_articleshow%2F115839186.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poll%20Body%20Invites%20Congress%20Delegation%2C%20Assures%20Review%20Of%20%26quot%3BLegitimate%26quot%3B%20Concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20a%20transparent%20process%20is%20followed%20with%20the%20involvement%20of%20candidates%20and%20their%20agents%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20the%20voting%20process%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20invited%20a%20Congress%20delegation%20to%20meet%20it%20on%20December%203%20over%20its%20apprehensions%20concerning%20the%20voting%20percentage%20in%20Maharashtra%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20had%20also%20raised%20some%20apprehensions%20about%20the%20EVM%20process%20after%20the%20Haryana%20assembly%20polls.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20poll%20panel%20has%20said%20it%20will%20review%20all%20legitimate%20concerns%20of%20Congress%20and%20provide%20written%20response%20after%20hearing%20the%20party's%20delegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%2C%20in%20its%20interim%20response%20to%20Congress%2C%20reaffirmed%20that%20there%20is%20a%20transparent%20process%20with%20the%20involvement%20of%20candidates%20or%20their%20agents%20at%20every%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20interim%20response%2C%20ECI%20also%20reiterated%20that%20there%20is%20a%20transparent%20electoral%20roll%20updation%20process%20with%20the%20involvement%20of%20political%20parties.%20The%20Commission%20has%20still%20assured%20Congress%20of%20further%20review%20of%20all%20its%20legitimate%20concerns%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20issue%20raised%20by%20Congress%20regarding%20voter%20turnout%20data%2C%20EC%20asserted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20discrepancy%20in%20voter%20turnout%20data%20which%20is%20available%20with%20all%20candidates%20polling%20station-wise%20and%20is%20verifiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gap%20in%205%20PM%20polling%20data%20and%20final%20voter%20turnout%20is%20due%20to%20procedural%20priorities%2C%20as%20presiding%20officers%20perform%20multiple%20statutory%20duties%20near%20the%20close%20of%20the%20poll%20before%20updating%20voter%20turnout%20data.%20As%20an%20additional%20disclosure%20measure%2C%20ECI%20press%20note%2C%20at%20around%2011%3A45%20pm%2C%20was%20thus%20introduced%20during%20the%202024%20General%20Elections%20and%20followed%20subsequently%20during%20all%20assembly%20elections%20thereafter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20poll%20panel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20on%20Friday%20alleged%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bintegrity%20of%20the%20entire%20electoral%20process%20is%20being%20severely%20compromised%26quot%3B%20and%20slammed%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20was%20discussed%20at%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20meeting%20and%20the%20party%20said%20it%20will%20launch%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20movement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20believes%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20entire%20electoral%20process%20is%20being%20severely%20compromised.%20Free%20and%20fair%20elections%20is%20a%20constitutional%20mandate%20that%20is%20being%20called%20into%20serious%20question%20by%20the%20partisan%20functioning%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Increasing%20sections%20of%20society%20are%20becoming%20frustrated%20and%20deeply%20apprehensive.%20The%20Congress%20will%20take%20up%20these%20public%20concerns%20as%20a%20national%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20who%20briefed%20the%20media%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Belectoral%20malpractices%26quot%3B%20also%20influenced%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CWC%20also%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20party's%20performance%20in%20Haryana%20has%20been%20contrary%20to%20all%20expectations.%20The%20INC%20should%20have%20formed%20the%20government%20in%20the%20state%20by%20a%20convincing%20margin%2C%20but%20it%20didn't.%20However%2C%20there%20have%20been%20electoral%20malpractices%20that%20influenced%20the%20result%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20have%20been%20overlooked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20CWC%20accepted%20the%20party's%20performance%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Bunexplainable%20and%20shocking%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Btargeted%20manipulation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20ECI%20seeking%20to%20know%20how%20voter%20turnout%20increased%20by%207.83%20percentage%20points%20after%20the%20official%20polling%20time%20had%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoubts%20are%20being%20raised%20from%20many%20levels%20on%20the%207.83%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20votes.%20Looking%20at%20the%20vote%20figures%20announced%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20there%20must%20have%20been%20long%20queues%20at%20the%20polling%20stations%20after%205%20pm%20on%20the%20day%20of%20voting.%20In%20how%20many%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%20were%20there%20long%20queues%20of%20voters%20after%205%20pm%3F%26quot%3B%20Patole%20said%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20apex%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20demanded%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announce%20%26quot%3Bevidence%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20video%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20official%20figures%20released%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%2065.2%20per%20cent%20voting%20was%20done%20till%2011.30%20pm%20on%20November%2020.%20The%20official%20figures%20released%20on%20the%20next%20day%2C%20i.e.%20on%20November%2021%20at%203%20pm%2C%20were%2066.05%20per%20cent.%20Where%20did%20the%201.03%20per%20cent%20discrepancy%20in%20the%20figures%20officially%20released%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20itself%20come%20from%3F%20How%20did%20a%20whopping%20nine%20lakh%20ninetynine%20thousand%20and%20three%20hundred%20and%20fifty%20nine%20votes%20increase%20in%20a%20single%20day%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20raised%20questions%20over%20EVMs%2C%20mentioning%20the%20rise%20in%20voting%20percentage%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20-%20comprising%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20faction%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20the%20Congress%20-%20won%20just%2046%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20winner%20with%20132%20seats%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20while%20its%20allies--the%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20the%20NCP%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar--won%2057%20and%2041%20seats%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections%20were%20held%20on%20November%2020%20and%20the%20results%20were%20declared%20on