.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-383805%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222740%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20focusing%20on%20social-emotional%20topics%20like%20mutual%20understanding%20and%20respect%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20children%20improve%20academically%20while%20also%20developing%20crucial%20life%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srishti.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20not%20just%20access%20to%20books%20that%20was%20a%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20was%20much%20more%20grave%20than%20we%20had%20imagined.%20Children%20in%20Class%208%20would%20not%20know%20the%20alphabet.%20They%20were%20not%20able%20to%20differentiate%20between%20a%20%E2%80%98d%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98b%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20recite%20poems%20in%20English%20because%20rote%20learning%20is%20embedded%20in%20us%2C%20but%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20what%20was%20being%20said.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fix%20this%2C%20not%20only%20does%20SABIA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335631%2Fassam-jorhat-transwoman-opens-free-libraries-for-queer-positivity-lgbt-empowerment%2F%5C%