D%20Srishti%20points%20out.%20By%20creating%20a%20space%20where%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20explore%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20voice%20their%20opinions%2C%20SABIA%20inculcates%20a%20love%20for%20reading%20and%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20world%20of%20stories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20rewarding%20experience%20to%20see%20the%20students%20actually%20be%20interested%20in%20books%20and%20learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suman%20Mishra%2C%20supervisor%20of%20Holy%20Star%20School%20in%20Malad%2C%20Mumbai.%20%E2%80%9COur%20school%20is%20located%20in%20a%20community%20space%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20a%20challenge%20in%20terms%20of%20space%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20dedicated%20library%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Suman%20is%20proud%20that%20the%20school%20has%20been%20able%20to%20accommodate%20a%20library%20for%20its%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20SABIA%20came%2C%20they%20turned%20our%20storeroom%2C%20where%20we%20kept%20supplies%2C%20into%20a%20small%20library%20by%20clearing%20half%20of%20the%20space%20and%20filling%20it%20with%20books%20our%20children%20could%20make%20use%20of.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20March%202024%2C%20about%20four%20volunteers%20have%20been%20visiting%20every%20Saturday%2C%20each%20working%20with%2010%20to%2015%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20children%20proudly%20holding%20up%20their%20drawings%2C%20created%20with%20the%20help%20of%20SABIA%20volunteers%2C%20showcasing%20their%20creativity%20and%20talent.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.