ortation%2C%20and%20even%20encourage%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20superblocks%20was%20introduced%20in%20Barcelona%20as%20part%20of%20its%202013-2018%20Urban%20Mobility%20Plan%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20redo%20120%20intersections.%20Currently%2C%20the%20city%20is%20working%20on%20redesigning%20one-third%20of%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20L%E2%80%99Eixample%20district%2C%20originally%20planned%20by%20Ildefons%20Cerd%C3%A0.%20Starting%20in%202022%2C%20the%20city%20is%20focusing%20on%20remodelling%2021%20streets%20by%202030.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20reliable%20EV%20infrastructure%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20component%20of%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20is%20its%20focus%20on%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F195571%2Fiit-kharagpur-innovation-deshla-electric-three-wheeler-recharge-home-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs).%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20city%20has%20worked%20hard%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20by%20investing%20in%20EV%20infrastructure%2C%20even%20offering%20incentives%20for%20EV%20owners.%20The%20city%20has%20installed%20over%201%2C000%20charging%20stations%2C%20for%20electric%20cars%20and%20given%20tax%20breaks%20and%20free%20parking%20for%20EV%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20also%20introduced%20electric%20buses%20and%20taxis%20into%20its%20public%20transportation%20network%2C%20further%20reducing%20emissions%20from%20traditional%20fuel-powered%20vehicles.%20This%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%2C%20particularly%20SDG%207%3A%20Affordable%20and%20Clean%20Energy%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20%E2%80%9Censure%20access%20to%20affordable%2C%20reliable%2C%