.com%2F372524%2Fpadmaja-rathore-empowering-communities-through-wildlife-conservation-in-jawai-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20conservationist%20from%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharvan%20(30)%20lives%20in%20Dhawa%2C%20a%20village%20near%20Jodhpur%20%E2%80%94%20a%20region%20where%20wildlife%20and%20humans%20have%20coexisted%20for%20centuries%3B%20but%20that%20delicate%20balance%20is%20increasingly%20under%20threat.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20used%20to%20take%20my%20books%20outside%20and%20study%20in%20our%20fields.%20It%20was%20so%20common%20for%20deer%20to%20interact%20with%20people%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20have%20to%20shoo%20them%20away%20every%20now%20and%20then.%20But%20today%2C%20if%20my%20kids%20want%20to%20see%20a%20deer%2C%20they%20have%20to%20go%20to%20a%20sanctuary%20or%20a%20zoo.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20our%20fields%20anymore%20because%20we%20have%20isolated%20these%20lands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecies%20such%20as%20the%20blackbuck%2C%20the%20Indian%20bustard%2C%20and%20even%20wolves%20once%20roamed%20freely%20across%20the%20arid%20plains%20and%20open%20grasslands.%20Sadly%2C%20many%20of%20these%20animals%20have%20faced%20a%20drastic%20decline%20in%20numbers.%20The%20wolves%2C%20once%20abundant%20in%20the%20area%2C%20have%20vanished%20altogether%2C%20and%20the%20blackbuck%20is%20protected%20under%20the%20Wildlife%20Act%2C%201972%2C%20and%20listed%20as%20an%20extremely%20vulnerable%20species%20by%20PETA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIdentifying%20challenges%2C%20spreading%20awareness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20wildlife%20crisis%20is%20the%20pollution%20of%20the%20Jojri%20River%2C%20which%20flows%20from%20Jodhpur%20to%20the%20south-west%20and%20stretches%20across%20the%20landscape%20for%20nearly%2083%20kilometres.%20The%20river%20is%20contaminated%20with%20chemical%20waste%20and%20untreated%20sewage%20from%20both%20industrial%20and%20domestic%20sources.%20This%20has%20created%20a%20dangerous%20situation%20for%20wildlife%2C%20particularly%20for%20animals%20that%20rely%20on%20the%20river%20for%20drinking%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20knew%20that%20the%20blackbucks%20were%20drinking%20the%20contaminated%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20tried%20to%20stop%20them%20by%20setting%20up%20some%20watering%20holes%2C%20but%20they%20still%20went%20back%20to%20the%20contaminated%20water%20because%20they%20had%20gotten%20used%20to%20drinking%20from%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203298px)%20100vw%2C%203298px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223298%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bluckbuck%20drinking%20the%20polluted%20Jogri%20river's%20water.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809.jpeg%203298w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-