ing%20and%20reuse.%20But%20recycling%20plastic%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20complexity%20of%20plastic%20is%20that%20you%20cannot%20intermix%20it.%20Different%20grades%20of%20plastic%20need%20to%20be%20processed%20separately%2C%20so%20that%20the%20end%20product%20is%20actually%20useful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20challenges%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20profits%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20research%2C%20and%20trial-and-error%2C%20the%20company%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20automotive%20industry%2C%20where%20high-grade%20plastic%20is%20used%20for%20manufacturing%20car%20parts.%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20began%20processing%20plastic%20waste%20from%20automotive%20manufacturers%2C%20refining%20their%20segregation%20process%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20plastics%20were%20sorted%20properly%20before%20being%20recycled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20thorough%20and%20diligent%20process%2C%20the%20company%20built%20expertise%20in%20plastic%20recycling%2C%20particularly%20in%20turning%20plastic%20waste%20into%20usable%20raw%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20trails%20were%20maddening!%20We%20even%20built%20small%20%3Cem%3Echulas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20experimented%20with%20melting%20small%20amounts%20of%20plastic%20in%20pans%2C%20using%20different%20methods%20at%20a%20very%20small%20scale%20to%20see%20what%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nitin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20'Plave%2C'%20a%20precast%20concrete%20ma