e%20patience%20to%20sit%20through%20it%20and%20instead%20played%20with%20other%20toddlers%20in%20a%20nearby%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Varijashree%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20concert%2C%20my%20father%2C%20H%20S%20Venugopal%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20apparently%20heard%20me%20scream%20something.%20Mind%20you%2C%20I%20could%20not%20even%20form%20a%20sentence%20at%20that%20time.%20But%20he%20later%20figured%20out%20that%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20say%20%3Cem%3ERaga%20Hamsadhwani%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20song%20being%20performed%20at%20that%20very%20moment%20was%20in%20%3Cem%3ERaga%20Hamsadhwani%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20home%20from%20the%20concert%2C%20her%20father%20was%20determined%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20what%20had%20just%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20at%20home%2C%20my%20father%20sang%20a%20variety%20of%20classical%20compositions%20from%20different%20composers%2C%20and%20as%20he%20tells%20it%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20form%20and%20structure%20of%20about%2040%20ragas%20(musical%20modes%20in%20Carnatic%20music)%20with%20whatever%20limited%20syllables%20I%20could%20pronounce%20at%20the%20time.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20observed%20early%20on%20that%20I%20had%20a%20%E2%80%98gift%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockq