E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20beginnings%20as%20a%20child%20prodigy%20in%20Carnatic%20music%20to%20recording%20%E2%80%98A%20Rock%20Somewhere%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20inimitable%20Jacob%20Collier%20and%20Anoushka%20Shankar%20%E2%80%94%20nominated%20this%20year%20for%20a%20Grammy%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Best%20Global%20Music%20Performance%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Varijashree%20has%20undertaken%20a%20remarkable%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20musician%20with%20a%20classical%20foundation%20who%20has%20since%20expanded%20into%20diverse%20cross-cultural%20and%20interdisciplinary%20styles%2C%20this%20Grammy%20nomination%20feels%20like%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20not%20just%20this%20song%20but%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316118%2Fbengaluru-interactive-indian-music-experience-museum-bollywood-songs-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusical%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20have%20undertaken%20so%20far.%20It%20is%20a%20milestone%20that%20reassures%20me%20that%20the%20direction%20I%20am%20taking%20%5Bcreatively%5D%20is%20good.%20Hopefully%2C%20this%20nomination%20fuels%20any%20independent%20artist%20out%20there%20to%20have%20a%20great%20and%20enriching%20creative%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMusic%20permeating%20through%20the%20walls%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20and%20my%20mother%2C%20T%20V%20Rama%2C%20an%20accomplished%20vocalist%2C%20were%20my%20first%20gurus.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20everything%20started%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20memories%20as%20a%20toddler%20are%20few%2C%20but%20they%20come%20back%20to%20her%20in%20flashes.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20vividly%20remember%20sitting%20through%20%3Cem%3EA