ing%20this%20process%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20system%20generates%20a%20paper%20slip%20for%20each%20vote%20cast%2C%20which%20can%20be%20cross-checked%20with%20the%20electronic%20results%20from%20the%20EVM.%20If%20discrepancies%20arise%2C%20the%20paper%20slips%20are%20considered%20final.%20This%20step%20guarantees%20the%20accuracy%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20voting%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Consolidation%20of%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20all%20rounds%20of%20counting%20are%20complete%2C%20the%20results%20from%20all%20counting%20tables%20are%20consolidated.%20The%20RO%20then%20declares%20the%20final%20result%20for%20each%20constituency%2C%20including%20the%20total%20number%20of%20votes%20received%20by%20each%20candidate.%20These%20results%20are%20thoroughly%20checked%20for%20any%20discrepancies%20or%20anomalies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Submission%20of%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20final%20tally%2C%20the%20results%20are%20sent%20to%20the%20ECI%20for%20official%20records.%20This%20step%20ensures%20the%20official%20compilation%20and%20validation%20of%20the%20election%20data.%20The%20ECI%20oversees%20the%20verification%20of%20all%20results%20and%20ensures%20that%20all%20records%20are%20securely%20archived%20for%20future%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Sealing%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20results%20are%20declared%2C%20the%20EVMs%20and%20VVPAT%20units%20are%20resealed%20and%20stored%20securely%20at%20the%20counting%20centres.%20These%20machines%20are%20retained%20for%20potential%20future%20verification%20or%20recounting%20and%20can%20be%20inspected%20if%20necessary.%20This%20ensures%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20transparent%20recount%20process%20should%20any%20concerns%20arise%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E9.%20Official%20declaration%20of%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20results%2C%20including%20the%20total%20number%20of%20votes%20each%20candidate%20has%20received%2C%20are%20officially%20declared%20by%20the%20RO.%20The%20ECI%20then%20compiles%20these%20results%20from%20all%20constituencies%20and%20announces%20them%20to%20the%20public%2C%20typically%20by%20evening%2C%20once%20the%20counting%20and%20validation%20processes%20are%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Findia-vote-election-counting-modi-1908222%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Findia-vote-election-counting-modi-1908222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20India%20Counted%20640%20Million%20Votes%20in%20a%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Newsweek%2C%204%20June%202024%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ftheprsblog%2Fhow-votes-are-counted-in-indian-elections%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20votes%20are%20counted%20in%20Indian%20elections%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Manish%20Kanadje%2C%2022%20May%202019%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fassembly-elections-2024-step-by-step-process-of-vote-counting-in-india-nc-124100800327_1.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssembly%20ele