0are%20properly%20prepared%20when%20speaking%20to%20inquisitive%20young%20girls%20who%20might%20have%20some%20interesting%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20also%20works%20closely%20with%20Deepika%20Godara%2C%20an%20advocate%20who%20engages%20with%20slum%20dwelling%20women%20and%20gives%20them%20a%20run%20down%20of%20their%20basic%20human%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CSure%20our%20country%20got%20independence%20in%201947%2C%20but%20the%20women%20are%20still%20not%20free.%20There%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20abuse%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358515%2Fwheat-stalk-painting-from-bahraich-uttar-pradesh-girls-training-early-marriage-entrepreneurship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20lack%20of%20proper%20healthcare%2C%20and%20so%20much%20misinformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.02.20-PM-1-1732171813-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Preeti%20Sharma%2C%20founder%20of%20Prazna%20Foundation%2C%20speaking%20to%20a%20group%20of%20slum%20women%2C%20educating%20them%20about%20menstrual%20health%2C%20hygiene%2C%20and%20breaking%20the%20stigma%20surrounding%20menstruation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.02.20-PM-1-1732171813-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.02.20-PM-1-1732171813-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.02.20-PM-1-1732171813-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWha